{
  "stem": "13315.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then when the Nuremberg Laws were put in force, then the director-- the new director called me and said, I'm sorry, you were a decent fellow here.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But, that's the law, we have to let you go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was a-- a cost accountant administrator.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That started in June '38.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Look, whenever I was in the streetcar or in the street I was in danger that one of the Nazis would not arrest me, but take me with him.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were just, how should I word it, free booty.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Look, first of all, there was a slight differentiation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To them, I looked Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "To others, I didn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It depends on your perception.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, but I never tried to hide it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] If somebody would ask me, naturally, I'm a Jew.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was, in a way, a Jew by default.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But you didn't dress differently or have any-- you didn't have the yellow stars?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[INTERPOSING VOICES]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not at that time, yet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like even in the concentration camp, we still didn't have the numbers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That came out later.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the concentration camp was a final experience.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You didn't know from one moment to the other what they could do and would do.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Yeah, we were Jews, the lowest scum of them all.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were a minority in the camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You had a lot of other people-- gypsies and other people.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
